title: Hour 2 - NFL Trade Deadline Watch, Will Deion Sanders Sellout?
itunes:title: Hour 2 - NFL Trade Deadline Watch, Will Deion Sanders Sellout?
description:
Dan wonders if Deion Sanders will be lured away from his job coaching at HBCU Jackson State by the Auburn opening. And he gets the latest information on the NFL trade deadline moves from insider Albert Breer.
